snippet.title: Sokoban gameplay (PC Game, 1984)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Sokoban, Dos PC game produced by Spectrum Holobyte in 1984 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/sokoban/670/
Solving a couple of puzzles in this addictive little brain teaser of a game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
